title: Too Faced Shadow Bon Bons Eyeshadow Palette 12 Shadows Candle Insurance Primer Lashgasm Mascara
description: As enticing as a box of scrumptious sweets Shadow bon bons is an sweets, indulgent treat for the eyes. 12 delicious shadows, a must-have ultra black mascara, a mirror, and a shimmering gold shadow primer make it easy to create a variety of fun eye looks, from sweet to sassy, subtle to dramatic. Designed as pure, sweet sex-appeal.

title: L'Oreal Telescopic Clean Definition & Lengthening Mascara, Black Brown 930
description: Clump-free. Perfectly-defined lashes. Patented no clump brush cleanly defines lashes. L'Oreal introduces Telescopic Clean Definition Mascara, for clump-free, perfectly-defined longer lashes. How It Works: The patented No Clump Brush lengthens lashes up to 50%. Ophthalmologist and allergy tested. Removes easily with soap and water. Suitable for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. Fragrance-free. Made in USA.

title: The Balm Cosmetics 9-Color Meet Matt Eyeshadow Palette
description: This professional quality and stylish eyeshadow palette from The Balm is a versatile matte palette that you can wear day and night, as liners and as all-over colors! Featuring nine large matte hues you're sure to find your perfect shade.
